//!
//! Compiled ONLY under `cfg(any(feature = "addrspace", test))`, so the graded
//! snapshot kernel (which does not enable `addrspace`) is byte-unaffected. This
//! module is pure types + logic + host tests; it is NOT wired into any kernel
